headline: Why Enphase (ENPH) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of home energy technology company Enphase (NASDAQ:ENPH) jumped 2.7% in the morning session after the company opened pre-orders for its new IQ EV Charger 2 and unveiled its IQ Bidirectional EV Charger architecture.
